data.description: This one checks all the boxes! You've got to see this low maintenance gem located in the sought after Model school district! Three bedroom two bath ranch with vinyl siding and two car carport on just under an acre. Lovely hardwood floors! Separate dining room! Lots of storage space inside, including a walk in closet in the master bedroom and a roomy kitchen pantry. Spacious front porch! The large back yard is fully fenced in and offers a huge two story storage building with power! And warm weather is just around the corner offering the opportunity to enjoy your sunroom and above ground pool! This one is a must see!
